description: The United Nations secretary general, Ban Ki-moon, said recent Iranian missile tests have caused alarm and concern, but he left it to the Security Council to determine any actions against Iran.
title: U.N. Reacts to Iran Missile Test
title_page: U.N. Reacts to Iran Missile Test - Video - NYTimes.com
text: The United Nations secretary general, Ban Ki-moon, said recent Iranian missile tests have caused alarm and concern, but he left it to the Security Council to determine any actions against Iran.
